                            <expan>Rege<ex>n</ex>sp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>, hat er uns
                                <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan></add> czü
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und also
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir ewr gnad und hilffe dar czü
                        wenden wöllet, daz <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gevange<ex>n</ex></expan> knecht ledig <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>.
